The paper discusses machine learning methods for improving classification performance by detecting when the minority answer is more likely to be correct than the majority answer. This topic is closely related to the fields of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and data science (cs.DS). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of ensemble methods, which are commonly used in the field of cybersecurity (cs.CY) to improve classification performance. Finally, the paper discusses the use of crowd wisdom, which is a topic that falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
